## List an App's Tasks

```
Definition
```

```http
GET /v3/apps/:guid/tasks HTTP/1.1
```

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.[your-domain.com]/v3/apps/:guid/tasks" \
  -X GET \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK

<%= yield_content :paginated_list_of_tasks, '/v3/apps/ccc25a0f-c8f4-4b39-9f1b-de9f328d0ee5/tasks' %>
```

This endpoint retrieves the tasks the user has access to.

